<%- include("../partials/header", { title: "Study Abroad Programme (SAP)" }) %>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

.sap-container{
  max-width:1200px;
  margin:auto;
  padding:40px 20px;
  font-family:'Poppins', sans-serif;
  line-height:1.8;
  color:#2f2f2f;
}

/* ===== Title Banner ===== */

.sap-title{
  background:#2d6f6d;
  color:white;
  text-align:center;
  font-size:36px;
  font-weight:700;
  font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
  padding:14px;
  border-radius:6px;
  margin-bottom:40px;
  letter-spacing:1px;
}

/* ===== Top Grid ===== */

.sap-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:40px;
  align-items:center;
}

/* ===== Images ===== */

.sap-img{
  width:100%;
  border:3px dotted #2db4ff;
  border-radius:6px;
  box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

/* ===== Quote Section ===== */

.sap-quote{
  font-size:19px;
  color:#444;
  font-style:italic;
  font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
}

.sap-quote strong{
  font-weight:600;
}

.sap-author{
  text-align:right;
  margin-top:12px;
  font-style:italic;
  font-weight:500;
}

/* ===== Middle Layout ===== */

.sap-middle{
  margin-top:35px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;
  gap:40px;
  align-items:center;
}

/* ===== Text Blocks ===== */

.sap-text{
  margin-top:22px;
  font-size:17px;
  text-align:justify;
  font-weight:400;
}

/* ===== Responsive ===== */

@media(max-width:900px){

  .sap-grid{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
  }

  .sap-middle{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
  }

}

</style>


<div class="sap-container">

  <!-- Title -->
  <div class="sap-title">
    Study Abroad Programme (SAP)
  </div>


  <!-- Top Section -->
  <div class="sap-grid">

    <!-- Left Image -->
    <img src="/images//hslu.jpg" class="sap-img">

    <!-- Quote -->
    <div class="sap-quote">
      “SAP at <strong>HSLU University</strong> gave me exposure to cutting-edge AI research and a chance to collaborate with international peers.  
      An extended opportunity of Research Internship aims to give full hands-on experience in cybersecurity specialization.”
      <div class="sap-author">– Vishesh Anand</div>
    </div>

  </div>


  <!-- Middle Section -->
  <div class="sap-middle">

    <div>

      <p class="sap-text">
        <strong>Kurapati Surya Manasa</strong> – RA2411028010049 attended GAIP Program at 
        <strong>NUS Singapore</strong> (Global Immersion Program) during December 2025.
      </p>

      <p class="sap-text">
        Four students from our department have been selected for a 
        <strong>Study Abroad Programme (SAP)</strong> opportunity at 
        <strong>Jeonbuk National University</strong> (often abbreviated as JGNU-QS Ranking #701–710 globally). 
        It is a public national university located in Jeonju, South Korea for the upcoming 
        <strong>2026 semester (March 2026 – June 2026).</strong>
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- Right Image -->
    <img src="/images/nus.jpg" class="sap-img">

  </div>


  <!-- Bottom Section -->

  <p class="sap-text">
    Two students from our department have been shortlisted for the prestigious research internship programme 
    at the <strong>Fields Institute for Research in Mathematical Sciences, Canada</strong>, scheduled for July 2026.  
    This fully funded internship provides hands-on research experience in advanced and applied mathematical sciences 
    under the guidance of internationally renowned experts.
  </p>

</div>

